TITLE: JWT Token Helper Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Example of using the getToken() helper function to verify and decrypt JWT tokens.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextauthjs/docs/blob/main/docs/configuration/options.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { getToken } from "next-auth/jwt"

const secret = process.env.NEXTAUTH_SECRET

export default async function handler(req, res) {
  const token = await getToken({ req, secret })
  console.log("JSON Web Token", token)
  res.end()
}
```

