TITLE: OAuth Provider Configuration Options in NextAuth.js
DESCRIPTION: Presents the TypeScript interface for OAuth provider configuration options in NextAuth.js. It includes various settings such as endpoints, profile handling, and client metadata.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextauthjs/docs/blob/main/docs/configuration/providers/oauth.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
interface OAuthConfig {
  wellKnown?: string
  authorization: EndpointHandler<AuthorizationParameters>
  token: EndpointHandler<
    UrlParams,
    {
      params: CallbackParamsType
      checks: OAuthChecks
    },
    { tokens: TokenSet }
  >
  userinfo?: EndpointHandler<UrlParams, { tokens: TokenSet }, Profile>
  type: "oauth"
  id: string
  version: string
  profile(profile: P, tokens: TokenSet): Awaitable<User & { id: string }>
  checks?: ChecksType | ChecksType[]
  clientId: string
  clientSecret: string
  idToken?: boolean
  region?: string
  issuer?: string
  client?: Partial<ClientMetadata>
}
```

