TITLE: Implementing Session Callback in NextAuth.js
DESCRIPTION: Example of session callback implementation showing how to customize session data. Demonstrates adding custom properties from JWT to the session object.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextauthjs/docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-v3/configuration/callbacks.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
callbacks: {
  /**
   * @param  {object} session      Session object
   * @param  {object} token        User object    (if using database sessions)
   *                               JSON Web Token (if not using database sessions)
   * @return {object}              Session that will be returned to the client
   */
  async session(session, token) {
    // Add property to session, like an access_token from a provider.
    session.accessToken = token.accessToken
    return session
  }
}
```

