TITLE: HTTPS Development Server Setup for NextJS
DESCRIPTION: Node.js server implementation for running NextJS with HTTPS support for local Apple Sign In testing.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nextauthjs/docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-v3/providers/apple.md#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: javascript
